utility.HTMLDisplayable

  • Packages that use HTMLDisplayable 
    Package Description
    assignments
    The assignments package contains the necessary files for Assignments, Assignment Submissions, Assignment Solutions, Courses, and Grading.
    cloudCoding
    The cloudCoding package contains files for basic program development through the cloud.
    testing
    The testing package allows for testing suites to be created and associated with assignments for automatic evaluation of code correctness.
